    Black Aracnia raises her claws above her head as the cowards retreat from 
the ship they moded there way in and out of. Victory was hers. With Thunder 
Hammer in pursuit, they wouldnt be back for awhile.
    "Quickstrike, check on your little assistant Darkmouse. I think shes 
injured. Your in command until my return. Paralysis and myself are going to 
get that pod!" She said, reloading her bowcaster.
    Paralysis croaks with delight and they head off. This time closeing the 
hatch.
